The Tokens of the Core Token Service.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TokenIdGenerator
    In interface for objects that can generate an identifier for a token if the existing one is null.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SAMLToken
    This wrapper class wraps up the various fields of the SAML tokens and contains them in a single class.
    Token
    A simple domain value responsible for modelling a Core Token Service Token.
    TokenIdFactory
    Responsible for generating Token Ids and for converting objects into their corresponding Token Ids.

Package org.forgerock.openam.cts.api.tokens Description

The Tokens of the Core Token Service. The Core Token Service is designed to accept a generic range of tokens, and convert these into instances of the Token class. If there are any other tokens that are as yet undefined, they can be stored here as appropriate.
